name: TenganMix
description:
■TenganMix

This merge model was created to draw a girl with beautiful eyes.

VAE is not built in, so use whatever you like.

The sample was created with the following settings.

・Blonde-haired girl : Euler a, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, Latent (bicubic), Denoising strength:0.5, ClearVAE

・Green-haired girl : Euler a, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, Latent (bicubic), Denoising strength:0.5, ClearVAE

・Black-haired girl : DDIM, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・White-haired girl : DDIM, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・Brown-haired girl : DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・Pink-haired girl : DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

　

　

■TenganMix

綺麗な瞳の女の子を描くために作ったマージモデルです。

VAEは内蔵されていませんので、好きな物を使用してください。

サンプルは以下の設定で作成しました。

・金髪の子：Euler a, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, Latent (bicubic), Denoising strength:0.5, ClearVAE

・緑髪の子：Euler a, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, Latent (bicubic), Denoising strength:0.5, ClearVAE

・黒髪の子：DDIM, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・白髪の子：DDIM, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・茶髪の子：DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE

・桃髪の子：DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale:7, Sampling Steps:30, R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, Denoising strength:0.55, ClearVAE
